This class cannot inherit from the community scoped item in a locked library

This LabVIEW class cannot access the referenced item because of security restrictions. The first time you establish access to a community-scoped item in a password-protected library, you must enter the password for that library. This prevents users from replacing a friended class on disk with another class of the same name. To correct this error, enter the password for the locked library in the Library Properties dialog box.
